      <p>A machining coolant centrifuge is an industrial <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc centrifuge</a> that effectively removes tramp oil and sediment from the coolant continuously. It is a mechanical separator that uses centrifugal force to separate water-based coolants from denser metal particles.</p>
